Invocation Name: scare my cat
des:
You can now scare your Cat using your Alexa. It contains multiple cat-fighting audios you can play on your Alexa to scare your cat!!

Options: 
- Next (To play the following audio)
- Previous (To play the previous audio)
- Start over (To start the audio from the beginning)
- Loop on (To play audio in the loop)
- Loop off (To turn the looping off)

Please leave your feedback if you like this skill. It will encourage us to keep creating more Alexa skills like this. Thanks
